entries.femaleVariant: Sorry choom, but there's no way you're getting the full rate. No way.
Did I or didn't I drop off the client at the spot?
Yeah, you did. With a slug in his belly and a broken leg.
Told him not to be a fuckin' hero. To stay back. But nooo, gonk wanted to show me he was Morgan fuckin' Blackhand.
I know, choom, I get it. I really do. But most clients are gonks. You gotta learn how to handle 'em, OK? Or else we get problems.
Anyway, not worth arguin' over. I'm docking ten percent, that's it. OK? Great.
